so that you can charge for it.

00:20:05.780 --> 00:20:09.640
So, it's like if you look at it
from the web perspective,

00:20:09.640 --> 00:20:13.010
it's your key to access
streaming services.

00:20:13.060 --> 00:20:17.120
Okay, apart from that,
we're looking into integration

00:20:17.610 --> 00:20:20.100
with or creating functions for MMS.

00:20:20.100 --> 00:20:25.850
Okay, integration to that and VIG is a
video interactive gateway which allows

00:20:25.880 --> 00:20:28.630
