00:20:46.390 --> 00:20:49.940
But we do have also other
partners that we have.

00:20:49.940 --> 00:20:52.850
we package along with our solution.

00:20:53.200 --> 00:20:54.150
Okay.

00:20:54.820 --> 00:20:59.140
Now, let's say we address
